"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Greetings frens, it's 2022, and I'm excited to turn up the dial to 11. I'm one of 250 unique Chubbicorns living in theÂ [Chubbiverse](https://www.chubbiverse.com/). Chubbicorns are rare, cute, loves giggles, and vomits rainbows. They also an amazing community of leaders that will change this space. Behind that chubbi face is a gigabrain community.\\n\\nChubbicorn80 is multi-cultural, multi-generational, and driven by the space in the middle. Web3 is exciting because it's the beginning of a shift in technology and culture. We get to be participants. We get to build it. We have the responsibility to fight for how this world is created.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/wjO7ywsAsXW42zdeeAeDO.png?height=1080&width=1080)\\n\\n## Main Focus in 2022\\n\\nMy focus may change as the world changes, but for now, my intentions are to focus on three main areas:\\n\\n1. **Add good vibes to this space**: Mental health should be on the same parity as physical health. The only way to survive this space is to care for ourselves. I intend on supporting a few small artists this year by buying their NFTs, and supporting their communities.\\n2. **Investing**: I'd like to invest in our future and want to find communities and companies that are building the future of Web3.\\n3. **Keep Going**: Thanks to [DRock](https://twitter.com/davidrocknyc) for the inspiration. This space is changing so quickly; we have to keep going. I'm going to create and build.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/oTcuuBW-uLp8mqSZOpFrI.png?height=1080&width=1080)\\n\\n## Guiding Principles\\n\\nWith great power comes great responsibility. As a Chubbicorn, my frens may interpret what I say, take action, and potentially cause harm to themselves or cause harm to the Chubbiverse brand.\\n\\n1. **Independence**: I am operating independently from the Chubbiverse. The Chubbiverse team does not pay me, nor am I formally endorsed by the team. My incentive is aligned with growing the value of the Chubbicorns and the Chubbiverse frens. When possible, I stay aligned to the direction of the team and community.\\n2. **Disclosure**: If I am compensated in any way, financially or free products, I will disclose that in my posts.\\n3. **Protect the Brand**: Although I am independent, I represent the Chubbicorns. I will not accept any projects or sponsorships that cause harm to the Chubbicorn brand.\\n4. **Own my Mistakes**: I will make mistakes; there's no way around that. If I make a mistake, I will own it as soon as possible and provide a full post mortem on it.\\n5. **Good Vibes Only**: One of the most important principles is to add good vibes to the community. Don't be a jerk, don't be an asshole. We are creating an inclusive community for all.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/EVotYPJODR1xE_OqrT-7v.png?height=1080&width=1080)\\n\\n## Welcome Frens\\n\\nThank you for following along with me on this journey. A warm welcome to the Chubbicorn80 family. You are amazing, you are special, you are loved.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rZA3fFmc6_7qOUrsTAXpj.png?height=1080&width=1080)\\n\\nAmazing art created by [FroggyCyborg](https://twitter.com/FroggyCyborg).\",\"timestamp\":1641065430,\"title\":\"Chubbicorn80 in 2022\"},\"digest\":\"T6pLui6q0863Fit6ZQrDfTi7lcUqLPhK190-5M28kS4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x91b8d9EA1C7c0f9660c72aA373a2a0D2b5fF28Ee\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IJkcymEyC_P2OuQgi1r5zw6-kOriHAZACsIUx9ePm10\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"1w5rDww07Vx38tCvL0ZlF0zDBq76Sr37H96xVPAE0sE\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"ZhyMEXpOsm_Ff-w0haaz6gyOsFPclA7RyaO3TB7hOm3lCyMrSKlM5z-M3XqAtXsHT7BbvOFV1n-IJP4Z7_6p7Q\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x96d8200bdc93cadd7c237b51b2da2204bd5d2a38cc0defc3e52b7ddf7010f7635576e107fe41cb96e8cf450ab77bdeb4acc414cb6a16558abc1468af7dffbb111c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IJkcymEyC_P2OuQgi1r5zw6-kOriHAZACsIUx9ePm10\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"1w5rDww07Vx38tCvL0ZlF0zDBq76Sr37H96xVPAE0sE\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"T6pLui6q0863Fit6ZQrDfTi7lcUqLPhK190-5M28kS4\"}"